    35	//!    the caller (`comprehensive_arena`) can use it as
    36	//!    `parent_state_root` when composing subsequent task-specific txs
    37	//!    (WorkTx, VerifyTx, ChallengeTx, TaskBankruptcy, etc.).
    38	//!
    39	//! `DriveTaskError::PendingAtomB` variant is REMOVED in this commit per
    40	//! the Atom A.1 forward-binding promise.
    41	//!
    42	//! ## Why minimum-viable (TaskOpen + EscrowLock only)
    43	//!
    44	//! Per `feedback_chaintape_externalized_proposal`: the chain records what
